Description of incident: RealSelf.com notified customers of a data breach when they company noticed unauthorized access to their consumer data located on their servers. The information compromised included username, email address and passwords.The company is encouraging customers to change their passwords which can be done by clicking on the link at https://www.realselft.com/user/forgotPasswordMore information:http://oag.ca.gov/ecrime/databreach/reports/sb24-59793
